**Welcome to theTown of Addison'sCitizen Self Service online portal!**

**This site provides the ability to apply for Single Trade Permits, request inspections on existing permitsand renew licenses.**

**Inspection Request :**

Please use this portal to request next day (tomorrow) or future inspections.

Same day Inspection requestmust be submittedBEFORE 7:00 am

**CONTRACTOR REGISTRATION(License):**

Town of Addison contractor registration informationmust be applied under/asthe State License holder name.

**Permit Linking:**

Create your user account on CSS andEmail: [Registrations@addisontx.gov](mailto:Registrations@addisontx.gov ?subject=Link%20Permit%20-%20CSS%20&body=I%20have%20created%20my%20CSS%20account%20using%20my%20email%20and%20wish%20to%20link%20my%20CSS%20account%20to%20the%20permit%20online.%20%0A%0AI%20am%20the%20authorized%20person%20from%20my%20organization%20to%20submit%20inspection%20request%20on%20this%20project%20and%20wish%20to%20get%20linked%20to%3A%0A%0APermit%20%23%3A%20%20%0A%0AJob%20Site%20Address%3A%0A%0AMy%20Email%20is%3A%20%0A%0AAs%20the%20GC%2FSuperintendent%20I%20acknowledge%20that%20I%20am%20responsible%20for%20requesting%20ALL%20my%20Sub%2FTrade%20Inspections%20for%20this%20project.%20%20%0A%0AThank%20you.%20%0A%0A%0A)in order to link your account online.

**Need Assistance?**Please contactthe appropriate Town of Addison Departmentregardinga specific permit or inspection.

****Building Permits and Contractor Registrations:** email**[permits@addisontx.gov](mailto:permits@addisontx.gov)**or call 972.450.2880**

****Planning and Zoning:** ContactKorriewith Development Services: **[kbecht@addisontx.gov](mailto:kbecht@addisontx.gov)**or call 972.450.2848**

****Sign Permits:**Contact Dale with Building Safety:**[djackson@addisontx.gov](mailto:djackson@addisontx.gov)**or call 972.450.2889**

****Fire Permits, Plans or Fire Sprinkler Systems:** please contact Fire Marshal 972.450.7221 or **[firemarshal@addisontx.gov](mailto:firemarshal@addisontx.gov)****

****Hotel Occupancy Taxes:** Please contact Ismael with the Finance Department:**[ivillalta@addisontx.gov](mailto:ivillalta@addisontx.gov)****

****Solid Waste and Water:** Please contact Ben with the Finance Department:****[**bnguyen@addisontx.gov**](mailto:bnguyen@addisontx.gov)******
